**Role Hierarchy:**
Administrator → Knowledge Curator → Knowledge Explorator

**Specialized Roles (Multi-Role):**
• Knowledge Reviewer = Curator + Review Powers
• Agent Operator = Curator + Agent Management
• Data Analyst = Explorator + Advanced Analytics

**Multi-Role Support:**
Users can have multiple roles simultaneously
Permissions = Union of all assigned roles

**Examples:**
• [Curator + Reviewer]: Can create AND approve
• [Curator + Agent Operator]: Can create + manage AI
• [Explorator + Analyst]: Read access + analytics

**Authentication:**
• Google OAuth 2.0 (Primary method)
• API Keys (Programmatic access)
• JWT Tokens (Session management)
